\newlabel{fig:domain_difficulty}{{2}{5}{Left: ARCG by problem domain. Logical reasoning tasks exhibit a significantly wider (more negative) gap than mathematical tasks. Right: ARCG by problem difficulty. The gap widens monotonically as problem difficulty increases}{figure.2}{}}
